      "content": "glitches and stuff dont just target specific years like that. it feels way too specific. like all the stuff i posted when i was working at that tech firm is what's missing. its like they're surgically removing my history from that time. it feels like a scrub. have u ever heard of companies doing stuff like that to people?",
